One of the medical students was discharged
C. Other patients
Patients, patient's family members & visitors PWH, PMH, PYNEH, QEH, TKOH,
Queen Mary Hospital & Tuen Mun Hospital 125 (123)
4 of the patients were discharged
Total admissions (A + B + C) 247 (242)
7 were discharged
8 patients with atypical pneumonia died recently in the following public
hospitals: KWH (2 patients); PMH (1); PYNEH (1); PWH (4).
The Department of Health's website on atypical pneumonia provides health
advice on the prevention of respiratory tract infection and latest
information on the cases in English and Chinese
.
[This represents an increase of 25 cases from yesterday's report. - Mod.MPP]
